### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8004
@pizzaStoreUrl = http://localhost:8001
@pizzaKitchenUrl = http://localhost:8002
@pizzaDeliveryUrl = http://localhost:8003
@pizzaOrderUrl = http://localhost:8005

### Start a new pizza order workflow
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/start-order
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderId": "1",
    "pizzaType": "pepperoni",
    "size": "large",
    "customer": {
        "name": "John Doe",
        "address": "123 Main St",
        "phone": "555-0123"
    }
}

### Validate pizza (approve)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/validate-pizza
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderId": "1",
    "approved": true
}

### Validate pizza (reject)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflow/validate-pizza
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "orderId": "1",
    "approved": false
}

### Get order status (from pizza-order service)
GET {{pizzaOrderUrl}}/order/123

